    {
      "id": "el_35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1193,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Wall:56→72(DIR), Days:6→8(INV)\nStep 2: M1xD1/W1 = M2xD2/W2\n  20x6/56 = M2x8/72\n  M2 = 20x6x72/(56x8) = 19.3\n\n  Variable   Change     Type\n  Wall       56→72      DIR → 72/56\n  Days       6→8        INV →  6/8\n  ? = 20 × (72/56) × (6/8) = 19.3\n\nTRICK:\n? = 20 x (72/56) x (6/8)\n= 20 x 9/7 x 3/4 = 19.3 → 20 men\nDIR: same order, INV: flip ratio\n\nAnswer: 20 men (rounded up) ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 35,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Wall:56→72(DIR), Days:6→8(INV)\nStep 2: M1xD1/W1 = M2xD2/W2\n  20x6/56 = M2x8/72\n  M2 = 20x6x72/(56x8) = 19.3\n\n  Variable   Change     Type\n  Wall       56→72      DIR → 72/56\n  Days       6→8        INV →  6/8\n  ? = 20 × (72/56) × (6/8) = 19.3\n\nTRICK:\n? = 20 x (72/56) x (6/8)\n= 20 x 9/7 x 3/4 = 19.3 → 20 men\nDIR: same order, INV: flip ratio\n\nAnswer: 20 men (rounded up) ✓",
