    {
      "id": "el_40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1193,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: More rice → More cost (Direct)\nStep 2: 36/54 = 1080/x\nStep 3: x = 1080 x 54/36 = 1620\n\n  36 kg ──→ Rs.1080\n  54 kg ──→ Rs.????\n  ? = 1080 × 54/36 = 1620\n\nTRICK:\nRate = 1080/36 = Rs 30/kg\nCost = 30 x 54 = Rs 1620\nSimplify: 54/36 = 3/2 → 1080x3/2\n\nAnswer: Rs 1620 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4000,
