      "groupIds": [
        "type_5"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: More rice → More cost (Direct)\nStep 2: 36/54 = 1080/x\nStep 3: x = 1080 x 54/36 = 1620\n\n  36 kg ──→ Rs.1080\n  54 kg ──→ Rs.????\n  ? = 1080 × 54/36 = 1620\n\nTRICK:\nRate = 1080/36 = Rs 30/kg\nCost = 30 x 54 = Rs 1620\nSimplify: 54/36 = 3/2 → 1080x3/2\n\nAnswer: Rs 1620 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
