      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1128,
      "width": 744,
      "height": 33,
      "text": "5 machines produce 500 units in 10 hours. How many\nmachines are needed to produce 800 units in 8 hours?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
