    {
      "id": "el_65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2061,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: More speed → Less time (INV)\nStep 2: Distance = 60x5/18x12 = 200m\nStep 3: Time = 200/(40x5/18) = 18 sec\n\n  60 km/h × 12 sec = distance\n  40 km/h × ?  sec = same distance\n  ? = 12 × (60/40) = 18 sec\n\nTRICK:\nInverse: ? = 12 x (60/40)\n= 12 x 3/2 = 18 seconds\nSame distance → speed x time = const\n\nAnswer: 18 seconds ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6500,
