      "groupIds": [
        "type_10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: More speed → Less time (INV)\nStep 2: Distance = 60x5/18x12 = 200m\nStep 3: Time = 200/(40x5/18) = 18 sec\n\n  60 km/h × 12 sec = distance\n  40 km/h × ?  sec = same distance\n  ? = 12 × (60/40) = 18 sec\n\nTRICK:\nInverse: ? = 12 x (60/40)\n= 12 x 3/2 = 18 seconds\nSame distance → speed x time = const\n\nAnswer: 18 seconds ✓",
